Monaco Editor 0.45.0 — vendored for Hermes F.4.3 Skill Proposals Studio.

Source: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/monaco-editor@0.45.0/min/vs/
Upstream: https://github.com/microsoft/monaco-editor

Files vendored under min/vs/:
  loader.js                                        (AMD loader)
  editor/editor.main.js                            (~3.3MB minified)
  editor/editor.main.css
  editor/editor.main.nls.js                        (default en locale)
  basic-languages/yaml/yaml.js                     (YAML syntax)
  base/worker/workerMain.js                        (web worker bootstrap)
  base/browser/ui/codicons/codicon/codicon.ttf     (icon font)

